{"tid":1433201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大持續教育學院 某學會 強迫入會及交會費","createTime":"2019-08-08T12:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:37:06.000Z","uid":116466,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"672abbbfbf0c241577d02360c6a6cf4cb0908325","tid":1433201,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"[借帳]<br />\n今日去註冊入學 真係好睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">浸大持續教育學院 垃圾學會SHL</span><br />\n逢讀呢科Higher Diploma in Management [ Sport and Healthy Living ]<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\">聲稱 報讀此課程學生 必須同規定 一定要入會</span><br />\n同旺角班健身中心班仆街有咩分別 拉人入會 迫比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n強制迫人入會 &amp; 強迫交$100會費 及購買一件垃圾風嬲<br />\n<br />\n垃圾入會Link <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScwXIgFo-J-Bp_uWYRQYQaD6q0iw8MPgyjksi8cJXXbCmMgFQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScwXIgFo-J-Bp_uWYRQYQaD6q0iw8MPgyjksi8cJXXbCmMgFQ%2Fviewform&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9QbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=e0121b4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScwXIgFo-J-Bp_uWYRQYQaD6q0iw8MPgyjksi8cJXXbCmMgFQ/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n眼看好多00後好多傻下傻下咁入左會<br />\n小弟寧願捐去義士基金都唔會入埋你地啲垃圾學會<br />\n強迫人入 真係嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b481bdc63946a94ed80c91dc207b14edcd8df7","tid":1433201,"uid":116466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af78d52f4bb8f1bc9d5453372254e56d647973c0","tid":1433201,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"推~~"},{"pid":"608f32c91ccdb1d3bc9f8c28c452b8d266e7c8e1","tid":1433201,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"